node.text: One of the sweetest photoshoots of December 🥹❣️ Let me know if you like this story 😊🫰
@antonina_kyrylenko це праааавда🥹 нехай більше таких клієнтів нам трапляється🥰
Боже, люблю людей, що не бояться дощу. Мокрий асфальт - так красиво 😍
@lina.mart_photography Thank you 🥰🫶 I hope to meet with you in London again 🫶
@radhastamiii I’ll be glad to photograph you again 🥹🫶 Need to catch up)
We have to book a shooting again with you soooon🥹♥️ amazing pictures !!!
Appreciate that!! 🥰 Thank you for trusting me 🥹🫶
such beautiful captures!!! memories we will treasure forever. thank you again!!! 🩵🙏🏻💍🫶
@_psh_ps thank you 🥹🫶 waiting for a moment when I can post more special photoshoots)
@aiviolet тоже об этом думаю 🥹 везет)) с вашего континента, кстати ребята))
My gorgeous niece and her fiancé! The pictures were absolutely stunning! ❤️
